data.title: Get USA Network
data.meta_description: Download this app from Microsoft Store for Xbox One. See screenshots, read the latest customer reviews, and compare ratings for USA Network.
data.text: The USA Network app is the best place to catch up on the most recent season of your favorite shows, watch live TV, and stream movies and past season content! Download the USA app now to watch full episodes of Suits, WWE Raw, Chrisley Knows Best, Temptation Island, AND MANY MORE! Get started by signing in with your TV subscription (cable, satellite or digital). The USA app supports most TV providers, including DirecTV, Spectrum, Xfinity, Dish, and AT&T. Sign up for an NBCUniversal profile within the app using your Facebook, Google, or email account to sync your favorite shows across our family of apps and to continue watching progress across all your devices. Youâ€™ll also receive three credits to watch episodes for free before signing in with your TV provider. COMMENTS OR QUESTIONS? Please reach out to support@nbctve.zendesk.com for assistance. Please note: Use of the app is limited to the United States and its territories. Video is accessible via 3G, 4G, LTE and Wi-Fi networks. Data charges may apply.
